-- Bloomberg's Robbins Discusses Working on Wall Street (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-07-09T13:51:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-09/bloomberg-s-robbins-discusses-working-on-wall-street-audio-.html
Bloomberg contributor Michael Robbins
discusses his experiences working as a "runner" at the  New York  
Stock Exchange. Robbins talks with Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and 
Courtney Donohoe on Bloomberg Radio's "Taking Stock." Michael 
Robbins had his first job on Wall Street as a "runner" in 1952. 
He retired in 2007 after more than 40 years as a member of the 
NYSE. The opinions expressed are his own.   (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 29:37
 